  <p class="specs">Weight: 8.8 oz &bull; Cushion: Moderate &bull; Cut: Low &bull; Drop: 6mm &bull; Support: Neutral &bull; Surface: Road</p>
  <p>The On Cloud Monster 3 is On Running's biggest, boldest daily trainer — built for runners who want maximum cushioning from On's signature CloudTec technology. Oversized CloudTec pods create a uniquely soft, spring-loaded sensation, with each pod compressing and rebounding independently with every stride. The Cloud Monster 3 sits on a wide, stable platform that makes it feel more grounded than its towering stack suggests. Weighing under 10 oz, it's one of the lighter options in the max-cushion category — great for high-mileage runners who want protective cushioning without dragging around a heavy shoe. Key specs: oversized CloudTec pods, Helion superfoam, 6mm drop, neutral, road.</p>
  
</div>

